snippet: Kevin Kisner kept up his impressive debut in China with a six-under-par 66 that gave him a two-shot lead over Russell Knox at the HSBC Champions in Shanghai.
abstract: Kevin Kisner takes two-shot lead over Russell Knox with six-under-par 66 at HSBC Champions in Shanghai; other golf scores noted.

headline.print_headline: Newcomer to Course Leads by Two
